t-d-1: Greetings Rookie! I am the First Knight of the Kingdom.
t-d-10: Now you are ready for a tougher challenge - Group raids!
t-d-11: To summon raids you need Monster Tusk. They drop from the Quest Bosses.
t-d-12: To assist you in raids there is a Legion with countless troops and generals at your disposal.
t-d-13: Let's summon your first unit. Follow me.
t-d-14: Now unit must be assigned to the Legion
t-d-15: It's time for you to learn about FLESH.
t-d-16: Every day there is a fixed amount of FLESH distributed across ALL players.
t-d-16i: To get FLESH you must have Raid Points (RP) earned.
t-d-17: To earn RP - participate in Group raids and Champion’s tourney.
t-d-18: Remember, more RP you have - more FLESH you will get at the end of the day.
t-d-19: Every raid has elemental weakness. It's important to use weapons matching it for extra 30% damage.
t-d-20: Every raid also has a weapon type weakness. If weapon matches you will gain another 30% damage!
t-d-21: Try to have all sets of weapons to take advantage of every possible weapon type and element.
t-d-22: Equipment is not the only way to become stronger. You can train your core stats too.
t-d-23: Good. Now get back to quests and level up once more!
t-d-24: It's time to conquer next quest!
t-d-25: You ran out of energy. Let me show how can you restore it back.
t-d-26: Now you can continue your journey.
t-d-27: It's time to choose your path.
t-d-28: If you want faster stamina recovery - choose Barbarian.
t-d-29: If you want faster energy recovery - choose Ranger.
t-d-3: To progress fast you must wear the best gear you can find.
t-d-30: If you want a balanced path - choose Mage.
t-d-31: Every day you will have 5 attempts for free. Make sure you spend them all!
t-d-32: This beast will boost your main character core attributes - Health, Defense and Attack. Keep it well fed!
t-d-33: Now get back to Onyx tower and get level 6. See you!
t-d-34: Every day you have set of tasks to complete.
t-d-35: Make sure you finish as many tasks as possible!
t-d-37: Trials - dungeons filled with powerful foes.
t-d-38: Like Onyx Tower - every day you will have free attempts to each kind of Trial. Use them all!
t-d-39: Group raids is the primary way of earning $FLESH tokens.
t-d-4: Let me show how to equip it.
t-d-40: The way it works is very simple! You win Raid Points each raid.
t-d-41: At the end of the day - you will get estimated amount of $FLESH tokens based on how many RP you earned before!
t-d-42: Summon more soldiers, assign to the legion, get back and finish the raid!
t-d-43: Grand Royale is a seasonal leaderboard with USDC prizes. Just play the game as best as you can and earn your prize!
t-d-44: Your soldiers must be trained too to help with tough raid bosses. Let's go.
t-d-45: Explore other ways of improving power of your army.
t-d-46: Alchemy lab is opened now. Let's check it out.
t-d-47: Try not to get lost - explorer every menu one by one.
t-d-48: Remember - every screen has a hint inside to explain you some basics.
t-d-5: Don't forget to grab your daily reward!
t-d-6: Onyx Tower is the main source of useful items which are gonig to help you to get stronger.
t-d-7: Your health and damage will be locked once you start a floor and can't be changed untill your exit or finish it.
t-d-8: Your free tries will be replenished every day.
t-d-9: Let me show you something within the walls of your castle...
